  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "The Croods: Prehistoric Party! features the lovable Croods family: Grug, Ugga, Eep, Thunk, Sandy, Gran and Guy, on a hilarious adventure through 30 unique and addictive party-style mini-games. Explore spectacular landscapes in an incredible new world filled with never-before-seen creatures as you battle your friends and family in this awesome adventure with up to four friends in multiplayer gameplay.",
